{"tid":182711,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳盧卡古拒續約拖肥 車仔紅魔料擲7億追獵","createTime":"2017-04-01T13:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T14:11:30.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3eadffdc5f2bec1c0af130d9fdf2b542a575dcd2","tid":182711,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】現以19球領前英超射手榜的射手盧卡古，被傳拒與「拖肥 」愛華頓續約，其舊東家車路士及「紅魔」曼聯亦有意回購該名23歲比利時國腳，據報此子身價已達7500萬鎊（約7.1億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然盧卡古仍有兩年合約在身，其經理人亦曾指「99.9%確定續約」，但多間英媒昨報道愛華頓開出隊史最高的14萬鎊（約133萬港元）周薪合約，已遭盧卡古拒絕；報道更指去夏求購失敗的車路士，有意再與曼聯等爭奪此子，據報愛華頓開出解約金為7500萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n卡尼或7周內復出撼兵工廠<br />\n<br />\n此外，盛傳收「咧」的熱刺射手哈利卡尼證實右足踝韌帶受傷，他季初曾因此傷休戰7周，熱刺昨於twitter指今次傷勢較輕，意味有望7周內復出，或可趕及4月30日英超主場迎戰「兵工廠」阿仙奴，該仗將是白鹿徑球場翻新前最後一場賽事。"},{"pid":"4623a38bb8f2605d949ad2c12e4d34601f13d041","tid":182711,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2f0c0e369484bd8ce89ef4ffecb0f33c294ec1","tid":182711,"uid":43666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2eab080dc4fb94c158649eb91e42acdc8ec7590","tid":182711,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"買盧卡古不如買我"},{"pid":"9557be7439548bd1407118fd52f598fa5db220e1","tid":182711,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"2596a7eaf299101630858236fc67dc2db6fb8cea","tid":182711,"uid":33719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:56:24.000Z","msg":"go mu la diu"},{"pid":"aaba2500840469e914c84dc1ee3ce1fc3e390575","tid":182711,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r